AVAILABLE IN DIFFERENT COLORS AND LENGTHS - Complements your home or business setup with multiple options to fit your technical and aesthetic needs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought this cable after I moved and lost some old cables - I have to say they are very well designed. Easy to use, great quality feel - gets the job done!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I purchased several of these eeros cat6 cables for my eeros routers … I removed the cables & plugged in the eeros cat 6 cable & it shut down both the modem & eeros router … shut down hard! After changing the cable with the same result I replaced the original cat6 cables. I had to call my internet provider to reset the modem. After several attempts the modem cleared & reset. I had to call tech support at Eeros, they had to log into my system to reset it.The eeros cables have issues !

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Very high quality and just what I needed. I am a cable snob and the lack of high-quality brand-name cables for these is slim. These are a win. Definitely will be replacing all my cables with these.
